{
  "stem": "12255.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they weren't governed by-- as far as internally is concerned, the British were only too pleased to allow them to organize themselves.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- there were many-- you've got to differentiate between the official authorities and the man, the soldier in the street, the officer in the street, as you might say, many of whom were highly sympathetic and helped them a great deal with materials and things like that.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they gradually became an organized, reasonably organized, community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I said, Rosensaft eventually became the chief and, and had a sort of council that worked with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and this is the way life was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a strange kind of society, but it was a society.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rabbi, you-- were all of the community Jewish at this barracks?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were still non-- still thousands of non-Jews as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So were still non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were gradually being sent away because they had no answer when they said they didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because many of them didn't want to go because they faced trouble from the Russians, and the Lithuanians, and so on who had themselves-- many of whom had been with the Nazis in persecuting the Jews and others-- didn't want to go back to Lithuania and to other parts of that part of the w-- Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were forced to go back by the Russians, by Stalin's command and demands from the Allies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many of them met a very, very sticky end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, well, now, politics-- politics played a very important part, British army-- British politics, not army politics.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- as I said, the people of other nationalities were being sent back.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
